Class CoursePane

  • java.lang.Object
    • view.CoursePane

  • public class CoursePane
extends java.lang.Object
    CoursePane class builds GridPane using JavaFX that will allow the user to add Course Objects to to courseList array. The CoursePane will also be able to display all the course that are Available in the courseList.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Caio Eugenio
